The Image Filtering Microservice
This is a Node-Express application which runs a simple script to process images.

You can:
1. Initialize this project using: `npm i`
2. run the development server with `npm run dev`

### Deploying your system
Follow the process described in the course to `eb init` a new application and `eb create` a new environment to deploy your image-filter service! Don't forget you can use `eb deploy` to push changes.

### You can access this server over the browser using DEV_URL(when running a local instance) or EB_URL(an elastic beanstalk instance running in the cloud).

EB_URL=http://harry-udagram-dev.us-east-1.elasticbeanstalk.com
DEV_URL=http://localhost:8082

http://{{EB_URL}}/filteredimage?image_url=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bd/Golden_tabby_and_white_kitten_n01.jpg